##################  SERVER  ###################

1. Create library files
 - socket usage (TCP only)
 - functions error wrappers
 - probably http protocol related

2. Create Server 
 - multi-threaded echo server 
 - update to web requests
 - Events
    - children management
    - shutdown
    - crash
    - other signals
 - processing http requests

3. Create Client
 - requests sending capabilities (like curl)
